<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Jack Travels: Transforming Worldwide Discovery</h1>
    <p style="max-width:720px;margin:16px auto 0">Jack Travels is the premier site for personalized trips, extensive travel knowledge, and special travel initiatives designed for inquisitive individuals and roamers.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section container">
  <div class="card" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 48px">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To ignite the desire to travel and provide exceptional, memorable, and enriching travel experiences for all adventurers.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:16px">We partner with local experts, seasoned travel guides, and communities worldwide to enhance cultural awareness and create life-changing travel routes.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Our Principles</h2>
  <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom:48px">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">✓ Authentic Experiences</h3>
      <p>We focus on authentic cultural interaction and genuine community participation in all our travel options.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">🌐 Cultural Links</h3>
      <p>Purposeful travel, notable findings, and encounters connecting travelers with international groups.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">🎯 All Are Invited</h3>
      <p>Trips and initiatives adapted for solo travelers, couples, families, and group adventures of any type.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">💫 Expert Assistance</h3>
      <p>We work with local specialists, esteemed tour guides, and travel companies to craft outstanding experiences.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.08),rgba(99,102,241,0.08));border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);margin-bottom:48px">
    <h2>Top-Tier Trip Planning</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:24px">We construct notable travel occasions upholding strict standards and skilled team to produce lasting and significant experiences for all attendees.</p>
    
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div>
        <h4 style="margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600">Our Commitments</h4>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;opacity:0.9">
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Expert travel organization and management</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Clear costs and moral travel methods</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Top-quality lodging and outstanding care</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Adventures for individuals, pairs, families, and teams</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 style="margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600">Travel Principles</h4>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;opacity:0.9">
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Ongoing enhancement and continuous improvement</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Steady integrity and equitable game rules</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Acknowledgment for competitive success and skill development</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:6px">Collaboration with the global snooker network</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Jack Travels' Unique Benefits</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">Fierce Competition</h3>
        <p>Our tournaments encourage skilled gameplay and skill improvement, helping players achieve top-level mastery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">Player Progress</h3>
        <p>Initiatives center on targeted objectives: technical excellence, strategic control, and championship performance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">Ongoing Innovation</h3>
        <p>We modify tournaments based on player feedback to maintain top global position.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">Honesty & Transparency</h3>
        <p>We promote fair participation, transparency, and respect—professional guidelines for all involved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section container">
  <div class="card" style="text-align:center;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto">
    <h2>Join Our Team</h2>
    <p>Jack Travels is dedicated to promoting worldwide discovery and cultural learning. As a traveler, guide, or travel lover, join us to enhance significant travel encounters globally.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px">
      <a class="btn" href="game.html">Join the Matches</a>
      <a class="btn ghost" href="index.html#contact">Contact Us</a>
